org.apache.ambari.server.security.authentication.kerberos

Class AmbariKerberosAuthenticationProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.security.authentication.kerberos.AmbariKerberosAuthenticationProperties

  • public class AmbariKerberosAuthenticationProperties
extends Object
    AmbariKerberosAuthenticationProperties is a container for Kerberos authentication-related configuration properties. This container holds interpreted configuration data to be used when authenticating users using Kerberos.

    If Kerberos authentication is not enabled for Ambari kerberosAuthenticationEnabled == false, then there is no guarantee that any other property in this container is valid.
